<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-PT">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Avvimo</title>
     <style type="text/css">
    *{
      margin: 0; 
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body{
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Tahoma;
      display:flex;
      align-content: center;
      justify-content: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .container{
      max-width: 420px;
      background: #f6f7fd;
      height: max-content;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .email-logo{
      color: #fff;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    footer{
      background: #f6f7fd;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    a{
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .name{margin: 30px 20px 0 20px;}
    button{
      outline: none; 
      border: none;
    }
    .email-text{
      padding:10px 20px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
    }
    .cordial-greetings{
      margin: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .email-title{margin: 10px 20px;}
    .location{font-size: 12px;}
    .logo-wrap{
      padding: 10px;
      background: #316CFF;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .social-media button{
      width:45px;
      height: 45px;
      margin: 2px;
      border-radius: 60%;
      background: #061b26;
    }
    .primary-color{
      background: #316CFF;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-link{
      padding:13px 20px;
      border-radius: 3px ;
      margin:30px 20px;
    }
    .img{
      height: 40px;
      max-width:150px;
    }
    .email-links button{
      color: #316CFF;
      margin: 10px 4px;
      background-color: transparent;
    }
    .trigger-link{color: #316CFF;}
    .location{margin: 20px 20px 0 20px;}
    .email-copy-rights{
      font-size: 12px;
      margin:0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .body{
      margin:0px 10px 10px 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius:0 0 10px 10px;
      background:#fff;
    }
    .text_left{
      text-align: left;
      margin: 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #a7a9ac;
    }
    .text_left .email-text,.warning-a .email-text{
      padding: 5px!important;
      word-break: break-word;
    }
    .warning{color: red;}
    .code{
      font-size: 30px;
      padding: 15px;
      color: #316CFF;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .warning-a{
      text-align: left;
      background: #FFF8E1;
      color: #FFB300;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin: 0 10px;
      display: flex;
    }
    
    .icon_l{
      padding:5px 5px 5px 0;
    }
    .email-text a{
      color:#316CFF;
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="email-logo">
          <div style="text-align: center;" class="logo-wrap">
            <img  class="img" src="{{logo}}" alt="logo" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <h3 class="name">Olá {{name}}</h3>
        <div class="email-body">
          <p class="email-text">Está tendo dificuldades em verificar a sua conta {{companyName}}?</p>
          <p class="email-text">Você se registrou, mas não concluiu a verificação, confirma seu email pra poder começar a investir.</p>
          <a class="" href="{{link}}" target="_blank">
            <button class="btn-link primary-color">Confirmar email</button>
          </a>
          <p class="email-text">
            <a class="" href="{{link}}" target="_blank">{{link}}</a>
          </p>
          <p class="cordial-greetings">Obrigado, atenciosamente equipe {{companyName}}.</p>
        </div>
      <footer>
        <div class="location">{{location}} </div>
        <p class="email-copy-rights">© Copyrights {{year}} {{companyName}}, Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
        <div class="email-links">
          <a class="" href="{{baseLink}}/">
            <button>Casa</button>
          </a>
          <a class="" href="{{supportUrl}}">
            <button>contacte-nos</button>
          </a>
          <a class="" href="{{baseLink}}/terms-condition">
            <button>Termos</button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>